{"tid":2326292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"培正小學教師被指踼保後改名任教　遭官媒狙擊　校管會成員：教師僅被截查","createTime":"2020-12-15T08:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:12:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49800ea2f7315f14fa180cab11ce3a9596d45ade","tid":2326292,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"教育界接連被建制派「狙擊」，《HKG 報》早前指香港培正小學有教師因非法集結被捕，其後改名繼續任教，內地官媒《人民日報》就事件指「必須嚴肅處理」、「終身封殺」。培正中學校監、培正小學管理委員會成員何建宗在同學會通訊的訪談中透露，該名教師僅被警方截查及記下資料，無被檢控，事件亦已向教育局通報，局方無要求解僱或停職，指社會上流傳「小題大做、渲染抹黑」的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%B8%BC%E4%BF%9D%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%99-%E9%81%AD%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E6%A0%A1%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1-%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%83%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B8%25BC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2583%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7f2d8e09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25B8%25BC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25